    "The pharyngeal endoderm development dataset provided by the original study 37 had already been filtered for high-quality cells and genes.",
    "Consequently, we directly quantified highly expressed genes using Scanpy's highly_variable_genes function.",
    "Then, we computed the PCA embedding and nearest-neighbor graph based on 30 PCs and 30 neighbors (n_pcs=30, n_neighbors=30).",
    "RealTimeKernel-based analysis.",
    "To study the pharyngeal endoderm development dataset with the RealTimeKernel, we followed the WOT tutorials to compute transport maps."
